</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Block light from headlight not being adjusted by placing light shield in front of the light.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Turn on headlights (low beams).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
